Abdomen (
Fig. 118 L
) Anterior parapods 34–57, 43 µm (8) long, each with about 20 longer claws. Posterior parapods 30–46, 42 µm (7) long, each with 5 claws, 5.5–7, 6.5 µm long. Dorsal anal tubules 16–39, 29 µm (6) long, 14–37, 24 (5) µm wide. Ventral anal tubules 34–57, 43 µm (6) long, 25–69, 39 µm (5) wide.
